#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:577
msgid "Root endpoint referencing deprecated `/api/*` paths"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:579
msgid ""
